  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueNode
  defaultText: 'Ah! Uh! I... I guess we are! And.. it''s a great moment! It is! I
    just... think... maybe we should... put it on pause... just until we fix the
    power! '
