  options:
  - optionText: It's hard to pump the brakes on my passion when you're around...
      but I'll do my best. You focus on looking pretty while I fix this up
    nextNode: {fileID: 0}
    choiceTrigger:
      text: It's hard to pump the brakes on my passion when you're around... but
